Process called "simulate_cpuinfo_content" returns String:
    Note: Simulate content of /proc/cpuinfo file for CPU information
    Let cpu_count be get_cpu_count_internal
    Let result be ""
    
    For i from 0 to (cpu_count minus 1):
        Set result to result with message "processor\t: " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as i with message "\n"
        Set result to result with message "vendor_id\t: GenuineIntel\n"
        Set result to result with message "cpu family\t: 6\n"
        Set result to result with message "model\t\t: 142\n"
        Set result to result with message "model name\t: Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-8650U CPU @ 1.90GHz\n"
        Set result to result with message "stepping\t: 10\n"
        Set result to result with message "microcode\t: 0xf0\n"
        Set result to result with message "cpu MHz\t\t: 1900.000\n"
        Set result to result with message "cache size\t: 8192 KB\n"
        Set result to result with message "physical id\t: 0\n"
        Set result to result with message "siblings\t: " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as cpu_count with message "\n"
        Set result to result with message "core id\t\t: " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as (i modulo 4) with message "\n"
        Set result to result with message "cpu cores\t: 4\n"
        Set result to result with message "flags\t\t: fpu vme de pse tsc msr pae mce cx8 apic sep mtrr pge mca cmov pat pse36 clflush mmx fxsr sse sse2 ht syscall nx rdtscp lm constant_tsc rep_good nopl xtopology nonstop_tsc cpuid tsc_known_freq pni ssse3 cx16 sse4_1 sse4_2 x2apic movbe popcnt aes xsave avx rdrand hypervisor lahf_lm abm 3dnowprefetch invpcid_single pti fsgsbase avx2 invpcid rdseed clflushopt md_clear flush_l1d arch_capabilities\n"
        Set result to result with message "\n"
    
    Return result

Process called "simulate_meminfo_content" returns String:
    Note: Simulate content of /proc/meminfo file for memory information
    Let total_memory_bytes be get_memory_internal
    Let total_memory_kb be total_memory_bytes divided by 1024
    Let available_memory_kb be (total_memory_kb times 80) divided by 100  Note: 80% available
    Let free_memory_kb be (total_memory_kb times 60) divided by 100  Note: 60% free
    Let buffers_kb be (total_memory_kb times 5) divided by 100  Note: 5% buffers
    Let cached_kb be (total_memory_kb times 15) divided by 100  Note: 15% cached
    
    Let result be "MemTotal:       " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as total_memory_kb with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "MemFree:        " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as free_memory_kb with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "MemAvailable:   " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as available_memory_kb with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Buffers:        " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as buffers_kb with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Cached:         " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as cached_kb with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "SwapCached:            0 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Active:         " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as (cached_kb times 3 divided by 4) with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Inactive:       " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as (cached_kb divided by 4) with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Active(anon):   " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as (free_memory_kb divided by 4) with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Inactive(anon):        128 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Active(file):   " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as (cached_kb divided by 2) with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Inactive(file): " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as (cached_kb divided by 2) with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Unevictable:           0 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Mlocked:               0 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "SwapTotal:             0 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "SwapFree:              0 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Dirty:                64 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Writeback:             0 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "AnonPages:      " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as (total_memory_kb divided by 8) with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Mapped:         " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as (total_memory_kb divided by 16) with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Shmem:                256 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "KReclaimable:   " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as (buffers_kb divided by 2) with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Slab:           " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as buffers_kb with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "SReclaimable:   " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as (buffers_kb times 3 divided by 4) with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "SUnreclaim:     " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as (buffers_kb divided by 4) with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "KernelStack:        8192 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "PageTables:        16384 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "NFS_Unstable:          0 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Bounce:                0 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "WritebackTmp:          0 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "CommitLimit:    " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as total_memory_kb with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Committed_AS:   " with message convert_integer_to_string with value as (total_memory_kb divided by 3) with message " kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "VmallocTotal:   34359738367 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "VmallocUsed:       32768 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "VmallocChunk:          0 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "Percpu:             2048 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "HardwareCorrupted:     0 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "AnonHugePages:         0 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "ShmemHugePages:        0 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "ShmemPmdMapped:        0 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "FileHugePages:         0 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "FilePmdMapped:         0 kB\n"
    Set result to result with message "HugePages_Total:       0\n"
    Set result to result with message "HugePages_Free:        0\n"
    Set result to result with message "HugePages_Rsvd:        0\n"
    Set result to result with message "HugePages_Surp:        0\n"
    Set result to result with message "Hugepagesize:       2048 kB\n"
